>L</keycap
></keycombo
></entry>
<entry
>استبدل الموقع</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap
>A</keycap
></keycombo
></entry>
<entry
>اعكس التّحديد</entry>
</row>

<row>
<entry
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Alt;<keycap
>Left</keycap
></keycombo
></entry>
<entry
